description:
This really pissed me off. At first I thought it was a coincidence, but then I really thought about it. I'm a pretty famous youtuber. 
 Of course whoever made this shit knows who I am. For those who don't know, a lot of famous people know who i am. A little while back there was a leak from adult swim of some of it's staff sharing my videos around for "comedy" ideas. Quotations around comedy because my video share not comedy. It's art. Stop claiming it as fucking comedy just because you disagree with what I produce and shit.

(Everyone Knows I pretty much own Sonic Underground because Sega DAMN sure doesn't own it anymore. Everyone knows that I'm the one who made this group of colors(Blue, Green, Pink, Red, Yellow, Orange, Purple, Light Blue) famous with my fucking videos.(Sonic, Manic, Sonia, Knuckles, bartleby, Mindy, Queen Aleena, Uncle Chuck.)
